abstract: Texas and Arkansas will play for the No. 1 spot in college football next Saturday in Fayetteville, Ark. But in at least one statistical area, the two unbeaten powers have nothing to shout about: their schedules.

abstract: Bravo Cabell Phillips! He has reincarnated Mark Sullivan. Doubtless there were a few errors in Sullivan's six-volume "Our Times," which covered the first 30 years of the century in America, and scholars would hardly look there for source material. It is just possible, too, that some younger historians have never heard of Sullivan and don't want to.
